<div class="pure-g question">

  <div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-16-24">

    <h1><%= current_screen.first_question.title %></h1>

    <p>In high-value industries, an offshore company can help a business avoid or evade hundreds of millions of dollars in taxes. <strong>One company in the Panama Papers allegedly evaded $100 million in taxes</strong> on the sale of oil blocks in Gabon, and has been taken to court to pay it back.</p>

    <p>Fill in the blanks in this taxmanâ€™s letter from the Panama Papers to discover how the company allegedly used its offshore structure.</p>

    <div id="words" class="fill_in_the_blanks_cont">
      <p>
        The fraud consists of the use of <span data-droppable data-position="0" class="word-gap"></span> established in <span data-droppable data-position="1" class="word-gap"></span>,
        without any true substance and whose <span data-droppable data-position="2" class="word-gap"></span> was to hold assets in Gabon and with the
        intention to sell them, with the primary goal of <span data-droppable data-position="3" class="word-gap"></span> to Gabonese <span data-droppable data-position="4" class="word-gap"></span>
        on the profits resulting from the sale.
      </p>
      <ul class="available_words">
        <% current_screen.first_question.options.each do |option| %>
          <li class="draggable"><%= option %></li>
        <% end %>
      </ul>
      <a href="#" class="restart" data-restart><i class="fa fa-refresh"></i> Restart</a>
    </div>


    <%= form_for current_screen.first_question.answers.new, url: answers_path(format: :json), data:{remote: true, answers: true, total: current_screen.first_question.right_options.length}, html: {class: "pure-form pure-form-stacked"} do |f|%>
      <%= f.hidden_field :took %>
      <%= f.hidden_field :question_id %>
      <%= f.submit "Sure? Let's check results", class: "pure-button pure-button-primary" %>
    <% end %>

    <div class="updated_hint" id="results" style="display:none"></div>

    <%= form_for current_session, url: session_path, remote: true, html: {class: "pure-form", style: "display:none", id: "next-screen"} do |f|%>
      <%= f.submit "Continue", class: "pure-button pure-button-primary" %>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-8-24 pos_relative">

    <%= image_tag 'doc_fillin.jpg', class: 'img_fillin' %>

  </div>

</div>
